Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣濕漉漉真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週全境終於進入梅雨時節了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的天氣會變得不太穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像強風  閃電  水位上等和塌方…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來一時半會停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣服什麼的麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去開門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  為什麼不直接回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  本來是打算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你用吹乾機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  我本來是直接回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我突然發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記帶鑰匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為求謹慎去檢查窗戶有沒有鎖好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從浴室窗戶直到二層的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我注意到的時候  警官已經在下面握著警棍嚴陣以待了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我向他解釋我就是這家的住戶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直到換班他都不放我走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…我看上去那麼像壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想被警棍指指看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想讓大人怕我一次看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是  小孩子也會怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕！實在太羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼同年同月出生  體格差異會這麼大？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也好  我想被人當做高中生看待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…我也想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我的衣服不合你身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁櫥裡面有爸爸的衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是只有兩個人一起生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不在那裡  還要靠裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠我那麼緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫仁那麼遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的仁真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天在女僕咖啡廳也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為健全的男人這是理所當然的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我為什麼會覺得難為情呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是姐弟之間親密的對話而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然的鬥嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此關係和睦的年輕…姐弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾只是為仁著想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太可愛  太挑逗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法直視才讓你別過來的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊！笨蛋——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對突然從天而降的姐姐說\N「哦  是這樣嗎」然後自然接受才不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她看成一個女性看待也是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這就簡直就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁斷的愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那麼可愛  那麼挑逗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法直視你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但吾可是仁的姐姐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流的是用這種眼光看姐姐的仁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實在是太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說起來  今天是仁的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你為了買這個蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才在女僕咖啡廳裡打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然  別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝這是第一次叫吾「姐姐」吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼吾的心中如此絞痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是和我不叫你「姐姐」的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深愛著作為一個女性的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是姐弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾也對仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好強大  像電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然是三次元的姐屬性  太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁你這個叛徒  快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因我愛著她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  天涯海角一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了  大鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話可以在客廳說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情我無論如何都想確認一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼看薙小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什麼怎麼看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望她的味覺能稍微正常點…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有證據的你的親姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然是沒有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可姐姐這點是不容置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前老爸就告訴我有個姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像記得你說你最近才知道薙小姐的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…剛才是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經和老爸取得聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後記得他說是自己的女兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你爸爸回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut Your Mouth！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這孩子念書太用功記憶混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣下去會感冒的  請先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就幫你準備替換的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我與仁要去準備晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝真是一點謊話都不會講！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編故事這方面交給吾不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的謊言不也漏洞百出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾有演技可以彌補  所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經公開是姐弟關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾就只能把仁的姐姐演到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾可不想因為汝的失誤而離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家父母不在只有小孩正是恰到好處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁又給我充分的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是生活費也有足夠吾用的份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁只要考慮如何讓吾更舒適的生活就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的事是騙人的？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙小姐利用這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁喜歡薙小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓吾繼續欺負汝的話  就多拿點錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來  再來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這沒種的  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒種的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁現在是被壞女人騙去當做金主了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(500,0)}頭目\N女人\N金主\N沒你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在這麼一張娃娃臉的下面卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾來馴服汝  汝這隻雜種狗  雜種狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但我是不會屈服的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁就由我來守護！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大鐵  不用這麼小心翼翼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是薙做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是微波食品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然平時眼神就很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾看現在還是要扮對好姐弟給他看才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁  你真沒教養
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米粒黏在臉上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真髒啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼遭雷劈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣很浪費的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  俗話說一米宿七神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好感謝上天的恩惠才行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這裡還沾著一粒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我自己做得到  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那出戲是不是起到反效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可吾是照抄動畫裡的情節咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我還是有一件事情想確認一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…可這是我能隨意插手干涉的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間不是男女關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若傻乎乎地深入詢問的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好像是剛才從壁櫥裡拿出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  這個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是預訂參加五月地區展的樹精靈像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雕像的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像薙小姐啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像不像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  這個是薙小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事到如今也無需隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有所覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那尊像就是吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹之精靈即吾身  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是以薙小姐為模特做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼理解的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這尊像  到頭來怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個嘛…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能完成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你從神社幫我把神木要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那棵神木不是我去要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是因為仁你說想用小時候遇到的樹之精靈來做成作品…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  是我順手牽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  特意為了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是過意不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想為你的熱情主動貢獻點力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我才瞞著神社把順手牽來的神木…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝這遭天譴的小子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…既視感？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（※戳鼻孔是非常危險的一招，請絕對不要失敗。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：寬叔乃也想被戳嗎=_,=||）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順…順手牽來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施…施工人員說剩下的也只是焚燒掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得怪可惜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指用淨火供奉燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拜神時處理掉的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來給仁神樹的犯人原來是汝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝這小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼是小偷啊…我只是想給仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給吾閉嘴！ 汝把神樹當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼薙小姐會如此生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她是神秘現象狂熱者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太目中無人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會遭報應的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷取神物棲息之所者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會以很高的幾率被詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如遭遇事件或事故
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹病上身痛苦致死的例子也屢見不鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若是反省並謝罪的話也許會被神靈寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不抱以足夠誠意的話就沒用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用神樹刻像的仁已經遇到了奇怪現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有朝一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢…夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實得嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子被薙小姐說了那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電…電燈也點不亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有朝一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒跳閘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是這一片地區停電了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才薙用什麼嚇了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便說你將要遭到神罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙那傢伙做得是不是有點過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  來電了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  薙  還醒著呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  對大鐵做了啥壞事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙  給我醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉還不行嗎  道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然神社已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還來得及吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了！  對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您原諒我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起！  我反省！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您了  神啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子又在輕率行事了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不必道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣使用那塊樹幹是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說那麼做其實比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向人之因果致以謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  總覺得身上黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得昨晚的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾只是像平常一樣睡著  然後起來而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫做不記得啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天大鐵不是把倒下的你扛回來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來好像真是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和滿口假牙不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}（「そういえば」“說起來”與「総入れ歯（そういれば）」“全假牙”一音之差）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然相似但別混淆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  比你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你也倒下過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是對我隱藏著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  吾什麼都沒藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你是悄悄地出去嚇唬大鐵是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停手吧  他對妖怪什麼的很不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你倒下了那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就在想  你是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡亂地追問吾  不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞清楚汝身為凡人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理之徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙那傢伙說她什麼都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個被捲進落雷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…但我說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…薙有做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…總覺得回答就在嘴邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我果然還是說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼嘛  那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也有過啊  這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然她在倒下之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我他妹的也亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的薙小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被神仙附體了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人貌似也什麼都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也看不出來是裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕——好怕——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是神我也好怕——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓  不要看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  還不能過早就確定是神靈現象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的薙小姐說不必道歉也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是嚇我嚇過頭覺得對不住我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是她才來道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是逢場作戲的她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是演技
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我X你妹的想拉到啥時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即便是演技但意圖不明！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保持與仁的關係在企圖些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了  難道我不知不覺中已經中了她的毒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  仁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不來和我商量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個…和那個女人的關係就那麼重要嗎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御廚和大鐵君的樣子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是打架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那兩個人看起來都挺不對勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  大鐵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  仁和大鐵君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁  我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢  聽不太清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望聽到你親口對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  大鐵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法回應你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  仁！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人陷入麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太少見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個總是一起來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大鐵君…昨天晚上在仁家裡過了一夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候發生了什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢～兩位少年共度一夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  學姐你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我只是對你…」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意那之後的台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…連副部長也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦  有薙薙在的話也不是只有他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有他們兩個也不會有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接問他們不久好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就算我問他也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\t(1,1,\fry-180)\t(1,750,\fry0)\t(2300,3020,\fry180)}ROUND  1　FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁絕對不會交給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神是不會寬恕你這種男人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
